	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The Action 53 carts use a region-free CIC, though not all games automatically adapt their speed, and some games' raster effects may break on a PAL NES unless they're specially coded.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


